channel.title: Good Clean Base For Starting A Project?
channel.description:
Hello community of Moparscape! I'm am sort of new to coding, and I thought that starting on a blank source and client would help me to learn java better. Can anybody recommend me a good clean base please? It would help if it had basic dupes fixed. Thank you so much!
P.S. I looked into a blank Project Insanity source and client, but people said Project Insanity sucked... If PI sucks, then what should I use?

item.title: Good Clean Base For Starting A Project?
item.dc:creator: @si_force Si Force
item.description:
@si_force wrote:

Browse the downloads section and chose a source that you feel comfortable working with. Everybody has their own comfort level, so I would advise making this a personal choice.
